name: 'Hey yoooo guys!' Necklace
description:
A Frankie and Delilah exclusive!

Show your affiliation to one of the coolest gangs of all time with our latest creation!

'Goonie' is made of 5mm thick black acrylic and measures approx. 10cm across and 3cm high.

Silver coloured chain measures approx. 46cm.

This necklace is limited to an edition of just 50 pieces and you will not find this anywhere else!!

name: Big Big Love Necklace
description:
A Frankie and Delilah original. 

If you've got something to say. say it loud!!

This is from a  limited run of just 50 pieces. We will not produce this again. So you can be safe in the knowledge that your necklace will be one of only 50 ever made.

The word 'Love' in 5mm thick red acrylic. Measures an enourmous 17cm by 8cm.

Available on gold or silver coloured chain.

Size of chain may differ from that shown.

Please specify when ordering colour and length of chain required and whether you would prefer chain with small or large (as picture) links.
